    Finds correlations between clusters from multiple distance metrics

    FindCommonCluster.Rd

    This function identifies and analyzes clusters using Spearman, Euclidean, and combined t-SNE data, generates cluster size histograms, and saves the plots.

    FindCommonCluster(ptmtable, toolong = 3.5, output_dir = "plots")

    Arguments

    ptmtable

    A data frame containing input data for cluster analysis.

    toolong

    A numeric threshold for cluster separation, defaults to 3.5.

    output_dir

    The directory where output plots are saved. Defaults to "plots".

    Value

    A list containing cluster groupings for each distance metric.

    Examples

    FindCommonCluster(ptmtable, toolong = 3.5, "output")
